Javinger.title: Javinger
Javinger.lyrics:
Verse 1:
Ginger's dancin' in my sneakers
Says they look better on her
But they look better on the speakers
Says 'Shut up Javier'

Chorus:
Ginger laughs at my jokes
And she smokes and she says she's vegan
She's drinkin' my coke and she's broke

Verse 2:
[Lyrics would go here]

(Bridge)
[Lyrics would go here]

Javi-family.title: Javi Family
Javi-family.lyrics:
Verse 1:
Family gatherin' round the table
Javi's stories never stable
But we love him just the same
Playing his musical game

Chorus:
Javi family, stick together
Through any kind of weather
Music binds us, music frees us
Javi family believes us

Verse 2:
[Lyrics would go here]

Break-Config.title: Break Config
Break-Config.lyrics:
Verse 1:
Code is broken, system's down
Config files scattered around
Javi's trying to make it right
Working through another night

Chorus:
Break the config, start again
Every error teaches when
Debugging life one line at a time
Making chaos into rhyme

Verse 2:
[Lyrics would go here]

(Bridge)
Stack overflow, but we don't quit
Every bug we're gonna hit

JavMarrage.title: Javmarrage
JavMarrage.lyrics:
Verse 1:
Walking down the aisle today
Javi's found his perfect way
Love and music in the air
Happiness beyond compare

Chorus:
Javmarrage, a celebration
Of love across the nation
Two hearts beating as one
New journey has begun

Verse 2:
Promises made with a song
Together we'll be strong

Javi-Love.title: Javi Love
Javi-Love.lyrics:
Verse 1:
In the morning when I wake
Every breath for your sake
Javi love is what I feel
Nothing else could be more real

Chorus:
Javi love, burning bright
Guiding us through darkest night
Every melody we share
Shows how much we really care

Verse 2:
Music playing in our hearts
Nothing ever tears apart
This connection that we've found
In every note, in every sound

(Bridge)
Love is music, music is love
Blessing sent from high above

jazz.title: Jazz
jazz.lyrics:
Verse 1:
Smooth saxophone in the night
Jazz notes floating, taking flight
Javi's playing something blue
Every riff feels fresh and new

Chorus:
Jazz is life, life is jazz
Every moment has its razz
Improvising as we go
Letting all our feelings show

Verse 2:
Upright bass and gentle drums
Magic music always comes

Tux.title: Tux
Tux.lyrics:
Verse 1:
Penguin walking, looking sharp
Tuxedo black from head to part
Linux running in his veins
Open source breaks all the chains

Chorus:
Tux the penguin, our mascot
Freedom's something that can't be bought
Every kernel, every line
Making technology divine

Verse 2:
Command line poetry in motion
Deep devotion to the ocean
Of possibilities that flow
When free software starts to grow

Chess.title: Chess
Chess.lyrics:
Verse 1:
Sixty-four squares, black and white
Every move requires insight
King and queen and rook and knight
Battle raging through the night

Chorus:
Chess is life, life is chess
Strategy conquers all the mess
Every game teaches something new
About what we're supposed to do

her-perspective.title: Her Perspective
her-perspective.lyrics:
Verse 1:
She sees the world with different eyes
Every truth and every lie
Javi tries to understand
What she needs, what she demands

Chorus:
Her perspective changes everything
Makes the sad songs want to sing
Every story has two sides
Love is where the truth resides

Verse 2:
Listening with an open heart
Every ending, every start
Seeing life through her view
Makes everything feel brand new

Castles-Of-Pride.title: Castles Of Pride
Castles-Of-Pride.lyrics:
Verse 1:
Built these walls so high and strong
Thought that I could do no wrong
Pride became my golden throne
Left me sitting all alone

Chorus:
Castles of pride come tumbling down
When real love comes around
Humble heart, the only way
To find peace at end of day

Verse 2:
Every stone was my mistake
Every wall was what I'd take
But love requires letting go
Of everything I thought I'd know

Original-Javier.title: Original Javier
Original-Javier.lyrics:
Verse 1:
Back to where it all began
Original Javier had a plan
Music flowing through his veins
Melodies like summer rains

Chorus:
Original Javier, still the same
Music is his only game
Every song tells his story
Every note reveals his glory

Verse 2:
Years have passed but dreams remain
Through the joy and through the pain
Music always finds a way
To brighten up the darkest day

(Bridge)
From the first chord to the last
Present, future, and the past
Original spirit burning bright
Guiding others to the light

Final Chorus:
Original Javier shows the way
Music lives another day
Every heart that hears his song
Knows exactly where they belong

ScaryJa.title: ScaryJa
ScaryJa.lyrics:
Verse 1:
Shadows dancing in the night
ScaryJa gives quite a fright
But underneath the scary mask
Love is all he'll ever ask

Chorus:
ScaryJa, don't be afraid
Every monster's heart is made
Of the same stuff as our own
Nobody's meant to be alone

Verse 2:
Haunting melodies he plays
Echoing through misty haze
Every ghost song tells a tale
Of love that will always prevail

GabbyBabbyFabbyDabby.title: Gabby Babby Fabby Dabby
GabbyBabbyFabbyDabby.lyrics:
Verse 1:
Gabby Babby loves to chat
Fabby Dabby loves his hat
Silly names and silly games
Everybody knows their names

Chorus:
Gabby Babby Fabby Dabby
Everyone's a little happy
When the nonsense starts to flow
That's when all our spirits grow

Verse 2:
Dancing to a rhythm wild
Playful like a little child
Every word a little gift
Making all our moods uplift

(Bridge)
Nonsense makes the most sense
When our hearts are feeling tense

Fumbled.title: Fumbled
Fumbled.lyrics:
Verse 1:
Dropped the ball again today
Fumbled everything away
But Javi taught me something true
Mistakes help make us something new

Chorus:
Fumbled, but not forgotten
Every failure's a begotten
Chance to rise and try again
Every loss can help us win

Verse 2:
Picking up the pieces now
Learning from mistakes somehow
Every stumble, every fall
Makes us stronger through it all
